ke@2x-220x127.png 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Rikke@2x-385x222.png 385w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-e2a4f6ad-1582-4792-ad35-82e473290176\">\n\n<h2>Rikke Berg Thomsen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>HEAD OF EMAIL MARKETING<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rikke works as Head of Email Marketing at Sleeknote. She regularly hosts live e-commerce trainings in collaboration with industry leaders like Campaign Monitor, Kissmetrics, AdRoll, and more.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:60%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/built-to-scale@2x-721x1024.png\" alt=\"built-to-scale@2x\" class=\"wp-image-104784\" width=\"541\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/built-to-scale@2x-721x1024.png 721w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/built-to-scale@2x-211x300.png 211w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/built-to-scale@2x-768x1091.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/built-to-scale@2x-380x540.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/built-to-scale@2x-600x853.png 600w, https:\